<P>
   WINETALK (Undated) _ The weekly wine column: Osar, a new wine
being released in Europe now and in the U.S. this fall: an Amarone
from the Veneto region of Italy that is made with an ancient grape
called oselata. By Frank J. Prial.
</P>
<P>
   WINE-TASTING (Undated) _ A capsule wine review.
</P>
