   MINOR-COLUMN _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ For one week, my family
did not set foot in one nationally owned corporate mega-chain
conglomerate superstore. No Eckerds. No Home Depot. No Texaco gas.
Allow me to elaborate. (Minor, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
