<P>
   LYNCH-COLUMN (Albany, N.Y.) _ When government does something _
just about anything, really _ it always costs more than it would
cost in the real world. Tsvi and Deborah Gold know all about that.
They got a bill for $$138 from the city for mowing their lawn. By
DAN LYNCH.
