<P>
   WONG-COLUMN (Oakland, Calif.) _ Kids and cops are usually an
oil-and-water combination. In recent years, however, some artists,
community activists and police leaders have worked to concoct a
smoother blend of those normally unmixable ingredients. By WILLIAM
WONG.
</P>
<P>
   JESSE-VENTURA (Walnut Creek, Calif.) _ While Minnesota Gov.
