is a neurotic Catholic schoolgirl called Mary Katherine Gallagher,
the alter ego of comedienne Molly Shannon. ``Superstar'' is the
story of a high school misfit. It is definitely a comedy, but it's
also a surprisingly sensitive and thoughtful treatment of teenage
alienation. By Joshua Mooney. 1,000 words + photo. BPI.
