<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-13 12:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5400 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a BC-CPT-NETWATCH12-COX &LR;      10-13 0936
