passage of a gay civil-rights employment bill, (the Employment
Nondiscrimination Act), hate-crimes legislation, lesbian and gay
adoptions and political appointments.
</P>
<P>
   SPOTLIGHT ON ... MARGARET CO. This week, we have transmitted the
first installment of New America News Service's ``Spotlight On...''
entertainment feature. ``Spotlight On ...'' is a lively Q&AMP;A
interview series with noted individuals whose achievements, stature
or influence put them in ``role-model'' positions. Celebrities from
the worlds of academia, entertainment, politics, science and sports
give readers a glimpse of their interests, hobbies, latest
accomplishments and some not-so-known facts _ like their plans for
ringing in the year 2000 _ in this short, fun feature. First up:
Comedian Margaret Cho.
</P>
