   Notable videos on sale
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  National Geographic: ``Hidden World of the Bengal Tiger'' and
``The Great White Bear,'' $19.98 each.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Kids: ``Blue's Clues: Blue's Big Pajama Party,'' $9.95.
``Rugrats: Make Room for Dil,'' $12.95.
</P>
<P>
   _Steve Murray writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
