<DOCNO> NYT19991013.0181 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-13 15:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5581 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-BBA-SOX-RIVALRY-2TAKE     10-13 1107
