</P>
<P>
   An officer interviewed by Professor Stephen P. Cohen and quoted
in his book ``The Pakistan Army'' endorsed this view. ``Nuclear
weapons are modern terror weapons and Islam enjoins us to strike
terror into the heart of the enemy,'' he said. &QL; 
