<HEADLINE>
ONLINE RESERVATION SYSTEMS SHAKE UP TRAVEL AGENT BUSINESS
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication notice: Also moving in `f' category.) 
 ( nk ) 
 By JOE SHARKEY   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR; To a visitor, Los Angeles can seem like Queens with dazzling
sunlight _ a vast, bewildering, high-density commercial and
residential expanse where navigation is aided by the fact that the
buildings are low enough to allow you to spot the topographical
landmarks and aim the car at least at a known point on the compass.
</P>
