</P>
<P>
   WYOMING-SAT-CUBIN. Rep. Barbara Cubin joined industry leaders
and consumer advocates to support new efforts to give rural areas
broader local and network television services via satellite. (600
words.) Barney McManigal
</P>
<P>
   WYOMING-HHS. Wyoming is the only state in the union that has
consistently failed to enforce a federal anti-tobacco law that
penalizes merchants for selling to minors, according to a study
released Wednesday by the Substance Abuse Policy Research Program.
</P>
<P>
   -30-
</P>
</TEXT>
