u w BC-HURRICANE-RELIEF14-1S     10-13 0698
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HURRICANE-RELIEF14-1STLEDE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BLACK CAUCUS RALLIES SUPPORT FOR CAROLINA FLOOD VICTIMS
 &HT;    Corrects Waters' state in 10th graf.
 &HT;    380&AMP;add.
