   ALA-GAMBLING (Montgomery, Ala.) _ In a sign that gambling will
not necessarily continue it spread in the South, Alabama has
rejected the lottery that the governor had pushed for. Voters
apparently listened to ministers who preached against it. By David
Firestone. 1,200 words.
</P>
