   (NYT40) ARCHANGELSK, Russia -- Oct. 13, 1999 -- RUSSIA-INQUIRY,
10-13 --Yuri I. Skuratov, who started an investigation of Kremlin
officials one year ago, is in the middle of a power struggle as
Russian elections near. ``I simply won't allow the case to be
destroyed,'' he says of the investigation which has offered
evidence suggesting, among other things, that Mabetex, which did
considerable work in Russia, bankrolled shopping sprees by
President Boris Yeltsin's daughters. (Jacqueline Mia Foster/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
