<P>
   (NYT51) NEW YORK -- Oct. 13, 1999 -- BBA-YANKS-REDSOX-8, 10-13
-- Scott Brosius of the New York Yankees colliding with catcher
Jason Varitek of the Boston Red Sox at home plate in the seventh
inning of Game 1 of the American League Championship Series on
Wednesday. Varitek dropped the ball just before Brosius arrived
home on a single by Derek Jeter to even the score 7-7. (Barton
Silverman/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT50) ATLANTA -- Oct. 13, 1999 -- BBN-METS-BRAVES-8, 10-13 --
Manager Bobby Valentine of the New York Mets looks exasperated near
the end of a 4-3 loss to the Atlanta Braves in Game 2 of the
National League Championship Series on Wednesday. The victory gave
Atlanta a 2-0 lead in the best-of-seven series. (Frank
Niemeir/Atlanta Journal-Constitution Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT49) NEW YORK -- Oct. 13, 1999 -- BBA-YANKS-REDSOX-7, 10-13
